Write a C program to calculateÂ factorial  using recursion

Input & Output Format:

Input consists of one integer.

Output consists of one integer followed by a string.
Sample Input & Output:

5

Factorial of 5 is 120

//coding

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int fact(int n)
{
    int i,c=1;
    for(i=1;i<=n;i++)
    {
        c=c*i;
    }
    return c;
}
int main()
{
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    cout<<"Factorial of"<<" "<<n<<" "<<"is"<<" "<<fact(n);
}
